data.description: Introducing 6019 Draycott Dr., a stunning residence that combines elegance with modern convenience. This spacious home features three generously sized bedrooms and 2 1/2 beautifully appointed bathrooms, making it an ideal choice for families or those seeking extra space. With approximately 1,600 square feet of living area, there's plenty of room to spread out and enjoy.    Step inside, and you'll be greeted by the tasteful updates that have transformed this property into a move-in ready haven. Gleaming hardwood floors extend throughout the main living spaces, providing a warm and inviting atmosphere. The open-concept design seamlessly connects the living, dining, and kitchen areas, making it perfect for entertaining and daily living.    The well-appointed kitchen boasts modern fixtures, stainless steel appliances, and ample counter space, making meal preparation a breeze. Retreat to the spacious bedrooms, where hardwood floors continue to meet your feet. The owner's suite includes a private ensuite bathroom for your convenience. Also enjoy a second floor loft for extra space to relax or converse.    6019 Draycott Dr. offers a peaceful backyard with a comfortably sized barn. Location matters and this property is conveniently located, making it an ideal place to call home. Make it yours today!
